href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"übersicht","title":"Übersicht","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das <em>HTML Element Section </em>(<code>&lt;section&gt;</code>) stellt eine allgemeine Unterteilung des Dokumentes dar, z.B. eine thematische Gruppierung des Inhaltes typischerweise mit einer Überschrift.&nbsp; Jeder <code>&lt;section&gt;</code> Abschnitt sollte identifizierbar sein, üblicherweise durch Einfügen einer Überschrift (<code><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/html/wg/drafts/html/master/sections.html#the-h1,-h2,-h3,-h4,-h5,-and-h6-elements\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">h1</a></code>-<code><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/html/wg/drafts/html/master/sections.html#the-h1,-h2,-h3,-h4,-h5,-and-h6-elements\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">h6</a></code> Element) als Kindelement des <code>&lt;section&gt;</code> Elementes.</p>\n\n<p>Zum Beispiel sollte jedes Navigationsmenü in ein <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code>&nbsp;Element eingebettet sein, eine Liste von Suchergebnissen und eine Anzeige einer Karte hat kein solch&nbsp;spezifisches&nbsp;Element und könnte daher in eine&nbsp;<code>&lt;section&gt;</code>&nbsp;eingebettet werden.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><em>Hinweis zur Benutzung:</em></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Wenn der Inhalt des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a> Elementes sinnvoll getrennt zu syndizieren ist, benutzt man stattdessen das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a> Element.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a> soll nicht als allgemeines Containerelement benutzt werden; dafür gibt es&nbsp; <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>. Insbesondere gilt dies, wenn die Einteilung ausschließlich für CSS-Zwecke gedacht ist. Als Faustformel gilt, dass ein mit&nbsp; <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a> ausgezeichneter Abschnitt auch in der Gliederung des Dokumentes erscheinen sollte.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">Inhaltskategorien</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Fließender Inhalt</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#sectioning_content\">Abschnitte</a>, greifbarer Inhalt.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubter Inhalt</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Fließender Inhalt</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag omission</th>\n   <td>Keine, sowohl das Anfangs- als auch das End-Tag sind erforderlich.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubte Elternelemente</th>\n   <td>Jedes Element das <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">flow content</a> erlaubt. Beachte, dass das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>&nbsp; kein Nachkomme des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a> Elementes sein darf.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM Schnittstelle</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element enthält nur&nbsp; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">globale Attribute</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Heading<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Bunch of awesome content<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel_2","title":"Beispiel 2","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"bisher","title":"Bisher","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Heading<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>some image<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>img</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"jetzt","title":"Jetzt","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Heading<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>some image<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>img</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/sections.html#the-section-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;section&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/sections.html#the-section-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;section&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/sections.html#the-section-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;section&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_kompatibilität","title":"Browser Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.10</td>\n   <td>4.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>2.2</td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>11.0</td>\n   <td>5.0 (iOS 4.2)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Andere mit Section verwandte Elemente: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Sections and outlines of an HTML5 document</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Übersicht","id":"übersicht"},{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Beispiel 2","id":"beispiel_2"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das HTML Element Section (<section>) stellt eine allgemeine Unterteilung des Dokumentes dar, z.B. eine thematische Gruppierung des Inhaltes typischerweise mit einer Überschrift.  Jeder <section> Abschnitt sollte identifizierbar sein, üblicherweise durch Einfügen einer Überschrift (h1-h6 Element) als Kindelement des <section> Elementes.","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<section>: The Generic Section element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"section","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<section> : l'élément de section générique","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<section>: 汎用セクション要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<section>: 일반 구획 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<section>","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<section>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<section>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<section>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/section","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/section/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section","title":"<section>: um Abschnitten zu erstellen"}],"pageTitle":"<section>: um Abschnitten zu erstellen - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}